app.title: Supplementary Materials
app.p: The following files are available online at http://www.mdpi.com/2223-7747/7/4/86/s1, Table S1: Additional detail on morphological, agronomic, and oil-related traits; Table S2: Eigenvalue and Eigenvectors of PCA; Table S3: Primer sequences and annealing temperatures. Supplemental file S1 reports additional information on cultivars used in genetic structure analysis and on best K determination.
